                <section class="about-section">
                    <h2>Who We Are:</h2>
                    <p>We are a dedicated team committed to making a real difference in the lives of people in Gaza. Every day, countless individuals face medical challenges and hardships that could be eased with the support of generous donors, compassionate hospitals, and organized associations. Our goal is to bridge that gap and create a network of help, hope, and healing.</p>
                </section>

                <section class="about-section">
                    <h2>Our Mission:</h2>
                    <p>Our mission is simple but powerful: to ensure that every life deserves a chance. We connect donors—whether individuals or organizations—with hospitals and associations capable of providing life-changing medical aid, prosthetics, or financial support. By facilitating these connections, we aim to restore dignity, health, and hope to those who need it most.</p>
                </section>

                <section class="about-section">
                    <h2>Our Values:</h2>
                    <p>We believe in transparency, compassion, and collaboration. Every donation is tracked and delivered responsibly, every story is treated with respect, and every partnership is built on trust. We strive to empower both those giving help and those receiving it, creating a community united by care and humanity.</p>
                </section>

                <section class="about-section">
                    <h2>Why We Do This:</h2>
                    <p>Life in Gaza can be extremely challenging, with limited access to medical care and essential resources. We know that even a small act of generosity—a prosthetic arm, financial support, or medical assistance—can transform someone's life completely. Our work is driven by the belief that together, we can turn despair into hope and challenges into opportunities.</p>
                </section>

